title: Printer's Sample Book, 1875
creditline: Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts
description: Small notebook with handwritten formulas for dyestuffs for printing textiles. Contains 624 small samples, mostly lawns.

tombstone.epitaph: Printer's Sample Book, 1875.Leather, paper, cotton.. Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts. 1945-55-27.
